      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"2. SPRINKLE JEAN is worth forgiving for her last effort when fifth (17.76) at this track over 305m. Has a good record at this journey. Has a strong record from this draw, notching two wins and three minor placings from five starts. Has winning claims on her best figures. 8. JEDDY SPAGHETTI missed the frame latest when fifth at Manawatu (21.25) but was a winner five back in the best time of the program. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Will be running home strong from out wide and can measure up this time. 7. BIG TIME LENA quickly away to win over the 318m at Manukau two runs back then settled forward again when finishing third at Manukau last start. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Can measure up. 3. WAVE DANCER did a good job to finish third last time out over 295m at Addington (17.06) in a Class 5, the second top-three finish on the trot.\",\"runners\":[2,8,7,3],\"exclusive\":false}",
